South African Mining Production Fell 5.1% in July From Year Ago

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-09-08T09:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/south-african-mining-output-fell-5-1-in-july-from-a-year-ago-agency-says.html
South African  mine production  fell
5.1 percent in July from a year earlier, Jean-Pierre Terblanche,
a spokesman for Statistics South  Africa , said by phone from
 Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
